entries.journal_entry_description: Do whatever Toff Henrou of the Skaak Tippers asks of you.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Toff wants you to defeat some Darkwalker scoffs.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Toff wants you to defeat some Darkwalker ruffals.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Toff wants an attack on the Darkwalkers. Go to their cave and defeat some Darkwalker ruffals and Darkwalker scoffs.
entries.task04_comm_message_text: Yeah, okay. I guess that's enough of that for now. Instead I need you to download some Darkwalker security codes from computers in their cave.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Toff wants you to download some security codes from computers in the Darkwalker cave.
entries.task06_comm_message_text: Right, that's well done. I got the codes. But we also need some security cards. You'll get those from Darkwalker sentinels.
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: Defeat Darkwalker sentinels until you've collected enough access cards.
entries.task08_journal_entry_description: Return to Toff Henrou and find out if there's anything more he wants you to do.
